    "summary": "The user asks for an economic overview of immigration, specifically probing whether the consensus favors benefits over costs. The assistant initially provides a balanced view, then leans slightly toward the consensus that benefits outweigh costs, but ultimately pivots to provide specific counter-arguments and named economists when challenged by the user.",
